Company Overview of Capital Growth Management. L.P.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Capital Growth Management. L.P. is a privately owned investment manager. The firm provides its services to charitable organizations, pension and profit sharing plans, investment companies, and high net worth individuals. It launches and manages equity mutual funds for its clients. The firm invests in the public equity markets of the United States. It was founded in 1990 and is based in Boston, Massachusetts. Capital Growth Management. L.P. operates as a subsidiary of Natixis Global Asset Management L.P.


